_local/
**/_local/

# whisper transcript 衍生格式（保留 .txt + .md 摘要即可，srt/vtt/tsv/json 過大且為重複內容）
courses/*/sources/transcripts/*.srt
courses/*/sources/transcripts/*.vtt
courses/*/sources/transcripts/*.tsv
courses/*/sources/transcripts/*.json
